      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRUISER MY UNCLE (1) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including three wins and two placings. Recorded a 1.75 lengths win (17.37) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Expected to go close. BLUE BUICK (2) was on speed settling but found some traffic when collided with another runner, finishing sixth (16.64) at Cannington in a Grade 4/5. Expected to feature on best. JUNK YARD HIPPY (3) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a win (17.35) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. AUSSIE SIGMA (4) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
